data.description: Price Reduced to sale! This lovely 3 bedroom/1 bath home sits on a large corner lot that is adjacent to scenic wetlands, home to Gray Herons, Ibis, Egrets, and other beautiful water fowl. This home features lots of natural light. Updates include freshly painted interior and exterior, beautiful Pergo flooring throughout, updated kitchen with quartz counter tops and all new stainless-steel appliances, new bathroom vanity and beautiful porcelain tiled shower. The spacious flex room with lovely French doors serves as a roomy master bedroom with a walk-in closet, a large home office, or a great bonus room. The inviting back yard patio extends your entertaining space for BBQs, friends, and family. This gem is close to highly rated schools and minutes from Siesta Key, Downtown Sarasota, UTC Mall, Sarasota Bradenton International Airport, Sarasota Memorial Hospital, Colonial Oaks Park Pickleball courts, The Palms Golf Club, and is just a few blocks from the popular Legacy Trail. To top it all off, a new roof (2020), new HVAC (2022), new hot water heater (2021) and best of all NO HOA and NO DEED RESTRICTIONS.
